**Add Credit Card to Account**

Open browser in your computer, and go to https://www.serverpointapps.com/ and click on Client Portal.
Once you login, click on **Menu** >> **Billing**
On right top side, click on "**Update Credit Card**" button
Write your new credit card information in the form, and click on "**check sign**" (ok) button.
```diagram

```

Reply for customer that want to add new credit card to their account

**Add Fund/Credit**

Under  **Billing** >> Click click on "**Deposit Funds**"

```diagram

```


**Using Credit Card**

Click on "**With Credit Card**" Tab and then fill up the form.
Then click on "**Tick**" mark to process charge from Credit Card.

```diagram

```

**Using PayPal**

Click on "**With PayPal**" tab to add fund using paypal.
Enter the amount they wish to deposit from their paypal account and click on "check sign" (ok) button. 
Then Click on the PayPal button to the right to proceed to PayPal.

```diagram

```

Reply for customer that want to add funds/payment to their account

**Pay Due Invoice**

Due invoice are list under **Menu** >> **Billing** >> Your due invoices.

Just click on '**Pay**' button to charge payment.

The payment will be charged from the registered credit card or from the available credit


Reply for the customer that want to clear the due invoice manually
